{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place onions and oil in mixing bowl then sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<b>.","Add curry powder and sauté <b>2 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<b>.","Add tomato purée, red wine, lemon juice, bay leaf, salt and pepper then cook <b>5 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Transfer to a large bowl and set aside to cool.","Once cool, remove bay leaf then place bowl on mixing bowl lid. Weigh into bowl mango chutney, mayonnaise, crème fraîche, cooked chicken and sultanas. Mix together thoroughly then serve with a scattering of freshly chopped coriander leaves."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g onions, thinly sliced (2 mm)","20 g olive oil","1 Tbsp curry powder","15 g tomato purée","80 g red wine","10 g lemon juice","1 bay leaf, fresh or dried","¼ tsp fine sea salt","¼ tsp ground black pepper","20 g mango chutney","150 g mayonnaise","150 g crème fraîche","500 - 600 g cooked chicken meat, cut in pieces (2 cm)","50 g sultanas","1 small handful fresh coriander, leaves only, chopped"]}],"id":"r82599","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-YM5xVz59rU0\/XZMt8AZLiTI\/AAAAAAAAZ_Q\/z1qtKdugnFYTelB8dD5vtPPzUmcU-SNiACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_4HOGh56oARAkZBvK.png","title":"Coronation Chicken","publishedAt":"2015-12-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"25.7 g","fat":"25.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"11.1 g","calories":"1921 kJ \/ 459 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","6 portions"]}